3. done! you can publish it or use it as you like\n\n## Attributions\n\nUse the awesome icons from [Lucide](https://lucide.dev/)\n\nbased on [astro-feather](https://github.com/gabrlyg/astro-feather)\n","readmeFilename":"README.md"}